# 6️⃣ Section Structure & Spacing

Vertical spacing between sections:

```
100px desktop
60px mobile
```

Hero top padding:

```
120px desktop
80px mobile
```

No cramped stacking.

Premium pages breathe.

---

# 7️⃣ Layout Rules

* Max width container: 1100px
* Centered content
* Single column layout
* No sidebars
* No navigation menu (single-action page)
* Sticky CTA button optional

---

# 8️⃣ Testimonial Design

* White cards
* Very light shadow
* Name in bold
* Role in muted gray
* Pull-quote slightly larger than body

No huge quotation marks.
No colored backgrounds.
Keep it institutional.

---

# 9️⃣ Bonus Section Styling

Category headings slightly tinted:

Add thin red line under each category heading (2px height).

Icons:
Simple line icons only.
No emoji in final design.
(Emojis are okay in draft copy, not final UI.)

